{
  "stem": "19921.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you would be-- get a little air in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nothing in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after we got in, the door was locked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And finally, about a day and a half later, the door was open in a remote area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the KBG open up the thing, with a pointed bayonet at-- like criminals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they supplied us with water, and some soup, and some bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was the first meal we had in about an hour-- in about a day and a half.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Of course, we took some bread with us-- whatever we had from that apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we didn't really starve, but it was just very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the water, which we didn't have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The only thing which we were missing really is water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the toilet facilities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was one baby there-- a little tiny baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The baby was not even half a year old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, they survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The whole family survived with the baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was at the baby's wedding at one point.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- and we got friendly with that family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we stayed friendly throughout the years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Of course, one of the-- as a matter of fact, the baby's father is a co-signer on my-- on-- as a witness to my wedding.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was also in the army, and I supported his regiment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So that's how close we got.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We survived both the war and survived the labor camp in Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in any event, after three weeks, we arrived to our destination, which was [RUSSIAN] Republic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nothing to see-- just tremendous trees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing there-- no industry, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only industry was forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dilapidated homes, single family, dilapidated homes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
